title: Football Manager 2014 Logo pack and kit pack
description:
Includes:
-kit pack season 12-13 (if u don't want kit pack SS12-13 running on fm14, donÃ‚Â´t extract the kit pack to Documents-->Sports Interactive-->Football Manager 2014-->graphics )

-logo pack (includes almost all logos from Clubs, Competitions, Continents and Nations)

How to install:

-Extract the files to Documents-->Sports Interactive-->Football Manager 2014-->graphics (if it doesn't 

exist, create one)

-Run Football Manager 2014 and go to: Preferences > Interface
Click "Clear Cache" button at the top. 
Click "Reload Skin" button at the bottom. 

There should be a box that pops up saying 'loading image data for the new skin'. Once this is done your 

graphics should be working within the game.

Enjoy!
